title.rendered: Achievement Unlocked! A&A Sets New Record of 55+ Companies in a Day!

content.rendered:
25th January brought in another huge milestone in the history of A&A Associates! A&A are proud to announce that the team has set a new record of 55+ companies in a single day. We wish Hearty Congratulations to our highly efficient sales team and supporting staff members. At A&A, we strive for success and now all eyes are on what’s next for the team and the company.
New goals and milestones to achieve will bring in new challenges but we keep moving forward and there’s no turning back!
